{"tid":2330550,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"本港上月發出接管或破產令數目創4年新高","createTime":"2020-12-18T06:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T06:48:03.000Z","uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"218972746383b70fa17a979a869bf1b6e3ba6a6b","tid":2330550,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:07:38.000Z","msg":"本港上月發出接管或破產令數目創4年新高<br />\n<br />\n本地, 財經 <br />\n發佈時間 18.12.2020 12:38 <br />\n最後更新時間 18.12.2020 12:38 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n破產管理署公布，本港11月提交破產呈請書數目按月回升18.8%，至719宗，結束連續5個月跌幅，按年上升近1%。今年首11個月累計上升7.3%，有7980宗。 11月發出接管或破產令的數目按月上升16%，有827宗，按年升逾28%，為4年新高。期內提交強制清盤呈請書按年上升逾72%，有57宗，按年升逾32%。上月發出清盤令有21宗，按月持平，按年下跌逾8%。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2371207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2371207&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=23d80eb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2371207</a>"},{"pid":"757dd37dbd28e077c91a87a05e2b4fdc3631da62","tid":2330550,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:08:26.000Z","msg":"又出成積表<br />\n某某人真係叻女，年年考第一，好打得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5e05e7d3dc914d06303a4164c1bab622364850","tid":2330550,"uid":1522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:08:38.000Z","msg":"個別事件, 無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac7ac02ce4f518aa2fc4bdb086ba2d5ad2c6cb8","tid":2330550,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:34:07.000Z","msg":"推出左国安法 泛民掃走哂 之鋒肥佬黎已經拉哂<br />\n點解香港仲有咁多人破產<br />\n政府同建制派點搞㗎，屌你老母，離哂譜"},{"pid":"a0c33e92241564d3b2b8710e5847189f5c5636c4","tid":2330550,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}